<subSubSection id="8C8E6575FF456AFAFCE99CDE1A9AB05C" pageId="190" pageNumber="952" type="discussion">
<paragraph id="C42B36FEFF456AFAFCE99CDE1A9AB05C" blockId="190.[788,1381,2542,2964]" pageId="190" pageNumber="952">
Subgenus Chrysopteron. 
<collectingRegion id="0650F81CFF456AFAFBA69CDE1A89B19A" box="[1114,1161,2695,2728]" country="South Sudan" name="Lakes" pageId="190" pageNumber="952">See</collectingRegion>
<taxonomicName id="03944D7DFF456AFAFB6F9CDE1B19B19A" authorityName="Temminck" authorityYear="1832" box="[1171,1305,2695,2728]" class="Mammalia" family="Vespertilionidae" genus="Vespertilio" kingdom="Animalia" order="Chiroptera" pageId="190" pageNumber="952" phylum="Chordata" rank="species" species="tricolor">M.tricolor</taxonomicName>
. One recent study placed M. scott as sister to 
<taxonomicName id="03944D7DFF456AFAFCEA9C861DA3B1CA" baseAuthorityName="Peters" baseAuthorityYear="1870" box="[790,931,2783,2808]" class="Mammalia" family="Vespertilionidae" genus="Myotis" kingdom="Animalia" order="Chiroptera" pageId="190" pageNumber="952" phylum="Chordata" rank="species" species="bocagii">M. bocagii</taxonomicName>
, while another found it to be basal to a group including M. welwitscha, M. rufoniger, 
<taxonomicName id="03944D7DFF456AFAFC249D7C1A65B074" baseAuthorityName="Peters" baseAuthorityYear="1870" box="[984,1125,2853,2886]" class="Mammalia" family="Vespertilionidae" genus="Myotis" kingdom="Animalia" order="Chiroptera" pageId="190" pageNumber="952" phylum="Chordata" rank="species" species="bocagii">M. bocagii</taxonomicName>
, 
<taxonomicName id="03944D7DFF456AFAFB809D7C1B1AB074" baseAuthorityName="A.Smith" baseAuthorityYear="1834" box="[1148,1306,2853,2886]" class="Mammalia" family="Vespertilionidae" genus="Myotis" kingdom="Animalia" order="Chiroptera" pageId="190" pageNumber="57" phylum="Chordata" rank="species" species="goudotii">M. goudotii</taxonomicName>
, and 
<taxonomicName id="03944D7DFF456AFAFCEA9D141DEFB05C" authorityName="Dorst" authorityYear="1960" box="[790,1007,2893,2926]" class="Mammalia" family="Vespertilionidae" genus="Myotis" kingdom="Animalia" order="Chiroptera" pageId="190" pageNumber="952" phylum="Chordata" rank="species" species="anjouanensis">M. anjouanensis</taxonomicName>
. Monotypic.
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
